s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badc0410d53fa9248c21513b1075344c05e15b6c","tid":323073,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T19:27:47.000Z","msg":"留名. <br />\n原來而家既共產黨, 唔係當年既共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解而家仲要放毛魔張相喺天安門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa4440604e30acf693619eab375db396561e012","tid":323073,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T20:10:13.000Z","msg":"如果當年國民黨有泛民同港豬已經可以咬死老毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話佢係鬼、背後國民黨支助，比位人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c123b63fd19e37b856c8eacf8af7710a06ba86","tid":323073,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T01:31:14.000Z","msg":"老毛如果見到今日嘅共產黨變成咁,一定死唔眼閉"},{"pid":"aacd5ef06423b20769b4cebb347a1ce76e18a4ad","tid":323073,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:09:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老毛如果見到今日嘅共產黨變成咁,一定死唔眼閉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢最撚想添啦，今日中國係完美極權國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84827efc01b658a2070ada7375ef0cb588153554","tid":323073,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老毛如果見到今日嘅共產黨變成咁,一定死唔眼閉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢最撚想添啦，今日中國係完美極權國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爭一樣，就係唔係老毛自己掌權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb1da85648ea7c63b26244c05747c0cd4c53098","tid":323073,"uid":61517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor